===Phrase===
'''Lord willing and the Creek don't rise''', '''Good Lord willing and the Creek don't rise'''

# {{colloquial}} {{US}} Barring unforeseen circumstances.  
#: This refers to the Creek Indians, not a small stream.  "Creek" should be capitalized.
#: ''Lord willing and the Creek don't rise, we'll have that new barn finished in time for the harvest.''


